Module mesakit.map.road.model
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.road.model

Class DeCartaRoadType

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.map.road.model.DeCartaRoadType
public class DeCartaRoadType extends Object
The definition of deCarta road types, which are used by client and converted from txd road types by vectormap or minimap. 
 RoadType Definition:
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Value |   Description
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
           1   |  Freeway
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     2   |  Arterial Road
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     3   |  Local Street
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     4   |  Terminal
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     5   |  Tunnel
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     8   |  Rotary Road
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     9   |  Ramp
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     10  |  Via
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     99  |  Sign
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     101 |  Intersection
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:
Jianbo chen
